{"type": "article", "id": 30047, "title": "《飞屋环游记》变身大头针小屋｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-07-24T22:51:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 15321, "name": "Sovrappensiero"}, {"id": 30562, "name": "LaSelva"}, {"id": 2291, "name": "Alessi"}, {"id": 30563, "name": "Incipit"}, {"id": 30564, "name": "OTOTO"}, {"id": 30565, "name": "Dor Carmon"}, {"id": 30566, "name": "Iván Zúñiga"}, {"id": 30567, "name": "Clive Roddy"}, {"id": 30568, "name": "Abi Alice"}, {"id": 30569, "name": "Hyela Lee"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160804170848YqbeVWQ1Al2BvDzK.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p>          </p><h3>Agata by Sovrappensiero</h3><p>吊灯不仅可以在灯罩上玩花样，米兰工作室 <a href=\"http://www.sovrappensiero.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sovrappensiero</a> 最近为 <a href=\"http://www.incipitlab.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Incipit</a> 设计的吊灯 Agata 就利用弯曲的铁管打造出了大胆的几何造型，兼顾了功能性与装饰性。和各种形状的纤细铁管形成对比的是与下方的榉木灯座以及由镜面玻璃制成的灯罩，不同材质的巧妙组合营造出了别样的光影效果。吊灯的挂绳长度与角度都能够自由调整，适用于各类室内环境。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.incipitlab.com/products/agata\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 320 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232632iRW0VkPbHSylezmd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.591687\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232632JvHD5U47qt8lGEh2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.964548\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232632y7XslJjURcvFPt89.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.008557\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607242326341HiG954lYBVLwycx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.399756\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607242326324Lbwr8S3pml1eWVG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.859413\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232633YduQ4FZRaHU3BAq1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.732274\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Tweet by Dor Carmon</h3><p>第一眼看到 Tweet 时你或许还会纳闷它到底是用来干什么的，实际上这个就像真的鸟儿一样直立的小物并不是什么装饰品，而是设计师 <a href=\"http://dorcarmon.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dor Carmon</a> 为特拉维夫品牌 <a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OTOTO</a> 设计的一款折叠型的削皮器。Tweet 侧面的三角形凸起就像是鸟喙，转轴则构成了眼睛的部分，整体造型小巧又富有趣味。折叠设计体现出了它的便携优势并且可以保护刀片不受污染，放在厨房内也不会占用过多空间。这款削皮器将于下月正式开始销售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607242325531JUwpqvtAkyhOsrW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.488998\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607242325537yR1a8tFSgokxBhC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.864303\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232553e8QKWHPfr0jUV9oz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.066015\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232553ksCraHilgSORTn1Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.682152\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232553izyWQc2aNpUClPMu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.795844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232553HlvhIXJe4FwO9P1N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Flota by LaSelva studio &amp; Iván Zúñiga</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.laselvastudio.es/\" rel=\"nofollow\">LaSelva</a> 工作室最近与 Iván Zúñiga 共同为墨西哥公司 Más 打造了一组名为 <a href=\"http://www.laselvastudio.es/#!flota/c245e\" rel=\"nofollow\">Flota</a> 的托盘系列，两种材质的搭配缓和了混凝土制品容易给人带来的冰冷感，加入了一丝柔和的气质。木质底座的存在以及随处可见的弧度软化了混凝土固有的坚硬感，使这些造型各异的托盘能够很好地融入居家环境当中。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232535K1aOeoH63jRGLVrM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639810\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232535xuSEMJ78GedILvK4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.545000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232536v8ySfjCg0qR2WmVM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702362\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232536L0NuIOzYBwbi39cA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.743719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232536aBp6Y3HgGKteUQmS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.038591\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Balloon Pin House by Clive Roddy</h3><p>除了钉在大头针板上，这些小文具也可以有别的去处：英国设计师以及工匠 <a href=\"http://www.cliveroddy.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Clive Roddy</a> 为它们设计了一个小屋，就像是从电影《飞屋环游记》中飞出来的迷你款。小屋的背面为钉子预留了一个开口便于固定，三根铁丝穿过圆柱形黄铜烟囱分别连接了一个球形软木，上面插有三百根大头针。用它来装点软木板或者是地图都能让人眼前一亮，只是放在办公桌上也非常有趣。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.cliveroddy.co.uk/shop/balloonpinhouse\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 25 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607242325180fU4uhcBMxSmsP9W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.346000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232520dyiZ47xSUNlenHgs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232521IyfNJOHtFkube5T0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232521ESYo1xC7MqyG5OJ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232521Chf7K95amI2HuZWQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232521x2DMFskbBE7l1P8O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.380000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Dotty &amp; Infinity by Abi Alice</h3><p>澳大利亚设计师 <a href=\"http://abialice.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Abi Alice</a> 为知名家用品品牌 <a href=\"http://www.alessi.com/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alessi</a> 打造了两款各具特色的挂钟 Dotty 和 Infinity。Dotty 的设计灵感来源于文具店内的那些五颜六色粘点，Alice 将圆形与直线搭配在一起打造出了极简的风格，而且会让人联想到古时通过观察天体运动确定时间的天文装置。Infinity 则采用了层层叠叠的几何结构，反映着时间不断变化永不停息的特质，摒弃了数字符号的表面只有两根蓝色的指针，有一种点睛之笔的感觉。<a href=\"http://store.alessi.com/usa/en-gb/catalog/detail/dotty-clock-wall-clock/abi11?ic=ujLeKA%3D%3D\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dotty</a> 和 <a href=\"http://store.alessi.com/usa/en-gb/catalog/detail/infinity-clock-wall-clock/abi10?ic=ZWVY%2Fg%3D%3D\" rel=\"nofollow\">Infinity</a> 的价格分别为 150 和 220 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232504OkATQgsZd48Xhwun.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.815625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232504hlX0bgNcjR17edfQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.815000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607242325048MsfKiwLZQSerJoT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.815000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607242325052qXlCn0dx1MYicEB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.745000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232505c5j4YEbCvdSqiN3u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Chris + Jessie by Hyela Lee</h3><p>茶、香蕉、舌头、窗户，你能想象这些其实是袜子品牌的包装吗？<a href=\"http://hyelalee.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chris + Jessie</a> 是美国设计师 Hyela Lee 创作的概念品牌，四种生活中常见的物品都作了特别的镂空设计，露出一部分色彩斑斓的袜子。Lee 希望通过这种出人意料的组合为平凡的日用品注入趣味，就好像品牌的标语那样：socks for fun。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232444LVC4I8RTs5hKWnqM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232445vR9cVxuPbMClEgI0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232444Zi35YIP0L9bJKvt8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232445fWU3Ry6cg7GabkoA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232445U3yeS2OPJvE8sfTd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232444Xy1D7FTRfJ6Usp0l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}